from me.

119
00:07:52,839 --> 00:07:55,720
(This pill can restore her five senses
for one day.)

120
00:07:56,279 --> 00:07:57,800
(At dawn the next day,)

121
00:07:58,600 --> 00:08:00,199
(she will pass away immediately.)

122
00:08:44,559 --> 00:08:45,240
Thank you.

123
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,399
I love you, too.

124
00:08:49,459 --> 00:08:52,815
♪The fate of past and present
is like clouds, like smoke♪

125
00:08:52,815 --> 00:08:56,345
♪Blown by the wind, yet it stretches on♪

126
00:08:56,345 --> 00:08:58,473
♪I only wish to be with you♪

127
